<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CKN Hub — Elite</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #C9952A;
    --gold-light: #E8B84B;
    --gold-muted: #8a6420;
    --bg: #0c0c0c;
    --bg-card: #141414;
    --bg-card2: #1a1a1a;
    --border: #2a2a2a;
    --text: #e8e8e8;
    --text-muted: #7a7a7a;
    --text-dim: #4a4a4a;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --danger: #c0392b;
    --success: #27ae60;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    min-height: 100vh;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 20px;
    height: 64px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--gold); }

  .nav-divider { width: 1px; height: 32px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 16px; }

  .nav-role {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .nav-switch {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-left: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none;
    border: none;
  }

  .nav-account {
    margin-left: auto;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ELITE BADGE */
  .elite-bar {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #000;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  /* VIEWS */
  .view { display: none; }
  .view.active { display: block; }

  /* DASHBOARD */
  .page { padding: 28px 20px; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 em { color: var(--gold); font-style: italic; }

  .sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 28px 0; }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .card-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .btn-gold {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #000;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-gold:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-muted);
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* STATS ROW */
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .stat { background: var(--bg-card2); padding: 20px 16px; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 28px; color: var(--white); }
  .stat-num .gold-plus { color: var(--gold); font-size: 18px; }
  .stat-label { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* PLAYER LIST */
  .player-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 18px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .player-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .player-item:hover .player-name { color: var(--gold); }

  .player-avatar {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: var(--bg-card2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .player-info { flex: 1; }
  .player-name { font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; color: var(--white); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .player-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }

  .player-status {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border: 1px solid;
  }
  .status-active { color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold-muted); }
  .status-new { color: var(--text-muted); border-color: var(--border); }
  .status-review { color: #e67e22; border-color: #7a4215; }

  .phase-dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  /* FORM */
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  label {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  input, select, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-card2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }
  input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus { border-color: var(--gold-muted); }
  select option { background: var(--bg-card2); }
  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; }

  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }

  /* WEAKNESS TAGS */
  .tag-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .tag.selected { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201, 149, 42, 0.08); }

  /* PROGRESS BAR */
  .progress-row { margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .progress-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .progress-name { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }
  .progress-val { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .progress-track { height: 3px; background: var(--bg-card2); position: relative; }
  .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--gold); transition: width 0.6s ease; }
  .progress-before { position: absolute; top: 0; height: 100%; background: var(--border); }

  /* POSITION CARD */
  .position-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
  .position-card {
    background: var(--bg-card2);
    padding: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .position-card:hover, .position-card.selected { border-color: var(--gold-muted); }
  .position-card.selected { background: rgba(201,149,42,0.06); }
  .pos-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .pos-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* DEMO REQUEST */
  .demo-request {
    background: rgba(201,149,42,0.06);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-muted);
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .demo-player { font-weight: 500; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .demo-detail { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .demo-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  /* QUOTE */
  .quote-block {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin: 28px 0;
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }
  .quote-text { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text); }
  .quote-attr { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 10px; }

  /* PHASE PILL */
  .phase-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .phase-1 { background: rgba(201,149,42,0.15); color: var(--gold); }
  .phase-2 { background: rgba(52,152,219,0.15); color: #3498db; }
  .phase-3 { background: rgba(46,204,113,0.15); color: #2ecc71; }
  .phase-4 { background: rgba(155,89,182,0.15); color: #9b59b6; }

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
    z-index: 200;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center; }
  .modal {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    width: 100%; max-width: 480px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    animation: modalIn 0.25s ease;
  }
  @keyframes modalIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .modal-header {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .modal-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; }
  .modal-close { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer; }
  .modal-body { padding: 24px; }
  .modal-footer { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: flex-end; }

  /* NAV TABS */
  .tab-bar {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    background: var(--bg);
    position: sticky;
    top: 64px;
    z-index: 90;
  }
  .tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    background: none;
    border-top: none;
    border-left: none;
    border-right: none;
  }
  .tab.active { color: var(--gold); border-bottom-color: var(--gold); }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--text); }

  /* SECTION */
  .tab-content { display: none; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  /* PITCH VISUAL */
  .pitch {
    background: #0d1f0d;
    border: 1px solid #1a3a1a;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px;
    position: relative;
    min-height: 200px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pitch-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .pitch-center {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 60px; height: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .pitch-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 14px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* NOTIFICATION DOT */
  .notif-dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-left: 6px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .empty-state-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.4; }
  .empty-state-text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .back-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none; border: none;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .back-btn:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .arrow-link {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gold);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }

  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .info-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-key { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .info-val { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }

  .weakness-chip {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.3);
    color: #e74c3c;
    margin: 3px;
  }

  .strength-chip {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: rgba(39,174,96,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(39,174,96,0.3);
    color: #2ecc71;
    margin: 3px;
  }

  /* SCROLLBAR */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); }

  .gold-num { color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">CKN<span>HUB</span></div>
  <div class="nav-divider"></div>
  <button class="nav-role">COACH</button>
  <button class="nav-switch">SWITCH ROLE</button>
  <button class="nav-account" onclick="showView('dashboard')">MY<br>ACCOUNT</button>
</nav>

<!-- ELITE BAR -->
<div class="elite-bar">ELITE TIER — INDIVIDUAL DEVELOPMENT ENGINE</div>

<!-- TAB BAR -->
<div class="tab-bar">
  <button class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('players')">PLAYERS</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('plans')">PLANS</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('positions')">POSITIONS</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('progress')">PROGRESS</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('demo')">DEMO REQUESTS<span class="notif-dot" id="demoDot"></span></button>
</div>

<!-- ============================
     VIEW: DASHBOARD / PLAYERS
============================= -->
<div id="view-main" class="view active">
  <div class="page">

    <!-- PLAYERS TAB -->
    <div id="tab-players" class="tab-content active">
      <div class="section-label">ELITE DASHBOARD</div>
      <h1>Know every player. <em>Build every plan.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">One-to-one development. Diagnostic first. Targeted to what each player actually needs.</p>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!-- STATS -->
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num" id="statTotal">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">PLAYERS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num" id="statActive">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">ACTIVE PLANS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num" id="statDemo">0<span class="gold-plus">+</span></div>
          <div class="stat-label">DEMO REQUESTS</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!-- PLAYER LIST -->
      <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:16px;">
        <div class="section-label" style="margin:0">PLAYER PROFILES</div>
        <button class="btn-gold" onclick="openAddPlayer()">+ ADD PLAYER</button>
      </div>

      <div id="playerList">
        <div class="empty-state">
          <div class="empty-state-icon">⚽</div>
          <div class="empty-state-text">No players added yet.<br>Add your first player to start building their development plan.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-block">
        <div class="quote-text">"Most 1-2-1 coaches do what they want, not what the kid needs. We build around what they lack."</div>
        <div class="quote-attr">CECIL NYONI · CKN FOUNDATION</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PLANS TAB -->
    <div id="tab-plans" class="tab-content">
      <div class="section-label">DEVELOPMENT PLANS</div>
      <h1>Weaknesses become <em>the programme.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">Every plan is built from the diagnostic. No generic sessions. No wasted time.</p>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div id="plansList">
        <div class="empty-state">
          <div class="empty-state-icon">📋</div>
          <div class="empty-state-text">Add a player and complete their diagnostic<br>to generate their development plan.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- POSITIONS TAB -->
    <div id="tab-positions" class="tab-content">
      <div class="section-label">POSITIONAL FRAMEWORK</div>
      <h1>What they need <em>in position.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">For players 13+ moving into 11v11. Position-specific expectations, not generic skills.</p>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div class="position-grid" id="positionGrid">
        <!-- Built by JS -->
      </div>
      <div id="positionDetail" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PROGRESS TAB -->
    <div id="tab-progress" class="tab-content">
      <div class="section-label">6-MONTH TRACKER</div>
      <h1>Show the <em>difference.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">Before and after. Coach logs it. Parent sees it. That's the proof.</p>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div id="progressList">
        <div class="empty-state">
          <div class="empty-state-icon">📈</div>
          <div class="empty-state-text">Progress tracking starts once a player<br>has an active development plan.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DEMO REQUESTS TAB -->
    <div id="tab-demo" class="tab-content">
      <div class="section-label">DEMONSTRATION REQUESTS</div>
      <h1>You know who it's for. <em>And why.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">When a demo is requested you know the player, the gap, and the level. Not a generic video. A purposeful response.</p>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div id="demoList">
        <div class="empty-state">
          <div class="empty-state-icon">🎯</div>
          <div class="empty-state-text">No demo requests yet.<br>Requests come from player profiles.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================
     VIEW: PLAYER PROFILE
============================= -->
<div id="view-profile" class="view">
  <div class="page">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="showView('main')">← BACK TO PLAYERS</button>
    <div id="profileContent"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================
     MODAL: ADD PLAYER
============================= -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="addPlayerModal">
